## Windsurf AI Development Rules

### Stack: {{stack}}

- Express 5 + Prisma + Zod layered architecture
- routes → controllers (Zod validation) → services → repositories
- Error middleware catches all — no try/catch in individual handlers
- Standard response: `{ success, data?, error? }`
- Test: Vitest + supertest for integration tests
- Prisma: always use migrations, never `db push` in production
